claim.claim-text:
22. A leash, comprising:
a strap with an attachment device at a bottom end thereof, for attaching to an animal's collar or harness;
a first sheath secured to said strap, said first sheath having a locking part connected thereto for securing said leash to an automobile seat belt fastener;
a second sheath secured to said strap; and
a storage pocket defined within said second sheath.
